query: How many transactions were made by customers who have a loan?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions t JOIN Accounts a ON t.account_id = a.account_id JOIN Customers c ON a.customer_id = c.customer_id JOIN Loans l ON c.customer_id = l.customer_id;

query: What is the total balance of accounts belonging to customers who also have a deposit?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(a.account_balance) FROM Accounts a JOIN Customers c ON a.customer_id = c.customer_id JOIN Deposits d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id;

query: What is the number of customers who have both a loan and a deposit?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.customer_id) FROM Customers c JOIN Loans l ON c.customer_id = l.customer_id JOIN Deposits d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id;

query: What is the total loan balance for customers who own at least one card?

query: What is the total deposit balance for customers who made at least one transaction?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(d.balance) FROM Deposits d JOIN Customers c ON d.customer_id = c.customer_id JOIN Accounts a ON c.customer_id = a.customer_id JOIN Transactions t ON a.account_id = t.account_id;

query: How many transactions were made by customers who belong to branch 1?

query: What is the total number of accounts for customers who belong to each branch?

query: What is the number of customers with more than one account?

query: What is the number of customers with more than one loan?

query: What is the number of customers with more than one deposit?

query: What is the number of customers who made more than 10 transactions?

query: What is the average loan balance for customers with deposits?

query: What is the number of accounts created before 2020 for customers with loans?

query: Count the number of transactions with amount greater than average per branch.
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions t JOIN Accounts a ON t.account_id = a.account_id JOIN Customers c ON a.customer_id = c.customer_id WHERE t.transaction_amount > (SELECT AVG(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions t2 JOIN Accounts a2 ON t2.account_id = a2.account_id JOIN Customers c2 ON a2.customer_id = c2.customer_id WHERE c2.branch_id = c.branch_id) AND c.branch_id = 123;

query: Count the number of deposits with balance above average per customer type.
